&lt;pre&gt;postgres=# SELECT TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE &apos;2020-02-07 16:00:00&apos; AT TIME ZONE &apos;GMT+8:00&apos;, current_timestamp, current_timestamp AT TIME ZONE &apos;GMT+8:00&apos;, version();
      timezone       |       current_timestamp       |          timezone          |                                                             version
---------------------+-------------------------------+----------------------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
